What I want to make: 

Personal Dashboard / Admin Panel — A PHP + MySQL backend with a jQuery-powered frontend. Think a simple CMS where you can create, edit, delete posts or entries. Hits SQL, PHP, JS/jQuery, and "web platform development" directly.

Should mainly manage personal Projects and Task Tracker 

Structure is as follows (for now): 
task-dashboard/
├── index.php          ← dashboard home
├── api/
│   ├── projects.php   ← CRUD for projects
│   └── tasks.php      ← CRUD for tasks
├── include/
│   ├── db.php         ← MySQL connection
│   └── header.php     ← shared nav/head
├── assets/
│   ├── style.css
│   └── app.js         ← jQuery logic
└── sql/
    └── schema.sql     ← your database setup

